              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
              <para>
                <text>For the purposes of <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">subsection (1)</citation></changeable>, sections 30E, 30F, and 30G of the State Sector Act 1988 apply as if they had been declared to apply by Order in Council under section 30C of that Act.</text>
