              <prov id="DLM3169203" irdnumbering="no" quote="1" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">CV 6</label>
                <heading>Crown Research Institutes</heading>
                <prov.body>
                  <subprov.crosshead quote="1">Income</subprov.crosshead>
                  <subprov quote="1" skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">1</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>An amount that a Crown Research Institute derives is income of the institute if the amount is for the purpose of producing outputs relating to public good science and technology.</text>
